# Cloudflare Pages (and Netlify) headers file.
# Security headers applied site-wide, plus long cache lifetimes for the
# static image/icon assets. Deliberately NO Permissions-Policy or CSP here:
# the app relies on the Screen Wake Lock and Vibration APIs and loads fonts
# from Google Fonts, and a restrictive policy would silently break those.

/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN

/favicon.svg
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=2592000
/favicon.ico
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=2592000
/apple-touch-icon.png
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=2592000
/og-image.png
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=2592000
